text: János Nyisztor (born 18 December 1887, date of death unknown) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
